  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your association with death has become so close that you gain the following benefits.</p><p><strong>Enhanced Wails.</strong> When you use your Wails from the Grave, you can deal the Necrotic damage to both the first and the second creature.</p><p><strong>Soul Interrogation.</strong> When you use the Question Spirit feature of a Soul Trinket you can ask it 3 questions and it must do answer the questions as truthfully as it can.</p><p><strong>Unending Phylactery.</strong> At the end of a Long Rest, a Soul Trinket appears in your hand if you don't have any Soul Trinkets, as the spirits of the dead are drawn to you. The spirit associated with this Soul Trinket is determined by the DM.</p>",
